(Unmute Sound for Optimal Experience)

Fragment 02 - Manifest
(From the BINARY EMOTIONS series)

"These images are just an outward manifestation of the vibrant life within the journey itself. We want to be a creative, generative ministry of vitality and consequence."

Manifest: It's dedicated to the realization of your inner light and the journey one takes to be whole. The utmost importance lies in "how" the journey is traversed and not "when". Manifest your dreams, Explore your path, and in return, you shall revive your light.
